keyMappings:
# Insert your preferred key mappings here
map <c-u> scrollPageUp
map <c-d> scrollPageDown
map <c-f> scrollFullPageDown
map <c-b> scrollFullPageUp
map zh scrollToLeft
map zl scrollToRight
map gh firstTab
map gp previousTab
map gn nextTab
map ga visitPreviousTab
map gl lastTab
